## Egress & Resource Summary

| Query | Data transferred | When |
|-------|-----------------|------|
| Following IDs | ~36 bytes × follows count | Once per page load |
| Journals (5 per page) | Same as main feed | On scroll |
| Likes/Bookmarks/Reactions personalization | Same as main feed | On scroll |
| Repost sources | Same as main feed | Only if reposts exist |

- **No new tables or migrations needed**
- **React Query `enabled` flag** prevents the following query from running when user is on the Writings tab
- **`staleTime: 5 min`** prevents refetching on tab switches within 5 minutes
- **Cursor pagination** ensures only 5 posts fetched at a time

